# =============================================================================
# Sentinel Health — Deployment env vars (example)
# Copy to .env if you need to override any of the defaults.
# Note: secrets live in module-specific .env files, not here.
# =============================================================================

# --- AWS (Sentinel Surgical) ------------------------------------------------
# Configure ~/.aws/credentials on the host (it's mounted into the surgical
# container at /root/.aws). Alternatively, you can export AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID
# and AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY here, but that's NOT recommended — keep secrets
# in ~/.aws/ where Docker can mount them read-only.

# --- OpenAI (Sentinel Insight) ---------------------------------------------
# The OPENAI_API_KEY is read from:
#   ../modules/insight/emotion-recognizer/.env
# Create that file with:
#   OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# Get a key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
